contentrichtext.text: {{Italic title prefixed|3}} '''USS ''San Diego''''' may refer to: * {{USS|San Diego|CA-6}}, originally the armored cruiser ''California'' (ACR-6) * {{USS|San Diego|CL-53}}, a light cruiser commissioned in 1942 in service throughout the Pacific War, and decommissioned 1946 * {{USS|San Diego|AFS-6}}, a combat stores ship in service from 1969 to 1997 * {{USS|San Diego|LPD-22}}, a ''San Antonio''-class amphibious transport dock, launched in 2010 {{Shipindex}} {{DEFAULTSORT:San Diego}} [[Category:United States Navy ship names]]
